    {"book":"2 Chronicles","chapter":10,"exaltation":0,"peace":1,"admonition":8,"contrition":2,"dominant":"admonition","rationale":"Rehoboam's harsh response divides the kingdom—a pivotal moment of political and spiritual fracture."},
