    {"book":"2 Chronicles","chapter":33,"exaltation":2,"peace":3,"admonition":7,"contrition":6,"dominant":"admonition","rationale":"Manasseh's extreme wickedness, captivity, repentance, and restoration—a dramatic conversion narrative."},
